Use the standard library
This is how to is_multiply_prime of a:
   Remember that count is 0
   Remember that i is 2
   Do this a times:
      When i is more than a, then:
         Leave the loop
      End when
      When remainder of a and i is 0, then:
         Increase count
      End when
      Increase i
   End do
   When count is 3, then:
      The answer is 1
   But, if not:
      The answer is 0
   End when
Now you know

>>> is_multiply_prime of 30
1
>>> is_multiply_prime of 5
0
>>> is_multiply_prime of 30
1